[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.376,
    "text": "[sighs]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.671,
    "endTime": 6.339,
    "text": "You know what we should all do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.215,
    "endTime": 8.8,
    "text": "Go see a musical."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.928,
    "endTime": 13.013000000000002,
    "text": "Sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.597,
    "endTime": 16.015,
    "text": "You know which one we should see?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.35,
    "endTime": 20.562,
    "text": "The 1996 Tony Award winner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.063,
    "endTime": 24.398,
    "text": "Do you happen to know the name of that one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.399,
    "endTime": 26.401,
    "text": "I don't know, um, \"Grease?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.236,
    "endTime": 29.404,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.781,
    "endTime": 33.574,
    "text": "\"Rent?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.575,
    "endTime": 34.909000000000006,
    "text": "Yes! \"Rent!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.286,
    "endTime": 37.746,
    "text": "Okay, so when do you want to go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.829,
    "endTime": 40.665,
    "text": "What? Oh, I'm sorry. I can't, I'm busy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.835,
    "endTime": 45.587,
    "text": "- Hey. - 'Hey.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.837,
    "endTime": 49.257000000000005,
    "text": "Man, it is so hard to shop for girls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.257,
    "endTime": 50.341,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.425,
    "endTime": 52.967999999999996,
    "text": "Yes, it is, at Office Max!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.638,
    "endTime": 56.806,
    "text": "What did you get her?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.641,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "A pen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.102,
    "endTime": 66.066,
    "text": "It's two gifts in one. It's a pen that's also a clock. Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.274,
    "endTime": 67.275,
    "text": "[laughs]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.442,
    "endTime": 69.151,
    "text": "You can't give her that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.152,
    "endTime": 71.029,
    "text": "- Why not? - Because she's not 11!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.614,
    "endTime": 74.824,
    "text": "And it's not the seventh night of Chanukah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.952,
    "endTime": 80.163,
    "text": "Okay, honey, what he means by that is.."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.246,
    "endTime": 81.997,
    "text": "Well, this is a very nice gift"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.082,
    "endTime": 84.79199999999999,
    "text": "maybe it's just not something a boyfriend gives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.793,
    "endTime": 86.21100000000001,
    "text": "Sure it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.461,
    "endTime": 87.962,
    "text": "She needs a pen for work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.962,
    "endTime": 89.714,
    "text": "She's writing, she turns it over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.714,
    "endTime": 92.05,
    "text": "Whoa! It's time for my date with Joey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.636,
    "endTime": 96.47,
    "text": "Alright, look, look. What.."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.471,
    "endTime": 99.4,
    "text": "What did you get for Angela Del Veccio for her birthday?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.516,
    "endTime": 101.518,
    "text": "She didn't have a birthday while we were going out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.601,
    "endTime": 102.93599999999999,
    "text": "For three years?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.939,
    "endTime": 108.982,
    "text": "Look, it's too late, and I got an audition."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.983,
    "endTime": 111.861,
    "text": "I can't shop anymore. I.."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.945,
    "endTime": 113.779,
    "text": "Alright, I will go out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.78,
    "endTime": 116.616,
    "text": "and I will try to find something for her, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.616,
    "endTime": 118.243,
    "text": "Thanks, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.243,
    "endTime": 119.619,
    "text": "And oh, while you're at it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.619,
    "endTime": 121.83,
    "text": "could you get her a card?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.871,
    "endTime": 124.916,
    "text": "Would you like me to write her a little poem as well?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.166,
    "endTime": 128.293,
    "text": "Or just get a card that has a poem already in it."
  }
]